Reichhold Chemicals Inc saidit is exploring the sale of its stake in its Europeansubsidiary Reichhold Chemie AG.    Reichhold Chemie Ag, headquartered in Rausen, Switzerland,had sales in excess of 75 mln dlrs last year. It is 83 pctowned by Reichhold. The rest is owned by German and Swissshareholders.    Reichhold said it is seeking the sale to focus on itsadhesives business. Reuter&#3;